@host = {{host}}
@token = {{token}}

### Listar compartimentos — primera página

GET {{host}}/api/v1/compartments/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar compartimentos — filtro por nombre icontains

GET {{host}}/api/v1/compartments/?name=fin
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar compartimentos — orden descendente por id

GET {{host}}/api/v1/compartments/?ordering=-id
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Sin token

GET {{host}}/api/v1/compartments/
Accept: application/json
